OL,3,CA 'significant and sustained police
OL,4,Cresponse is in place' after man was
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FStaffordshire Police have reassured
OL,8,Fresidents that that a 'significant and
OL,9,Fsustained police response is in place'
OL,10,Fafter a man was stabbed, while walking
OL,11,Fon a public footpath through Stafford
OL,12,FCastle golf course.
OL,14,FA man in his 60s was found on a bench
OL,15,Fnear the town centre after the attack
OL,16,Fby a member of the public at around.
OL,18,FPolice were called at 7pm on Thursday
OL,19,F(May 15) to Newport Road, close to the
OL,20,FCastle Golf and Leisure, following
OL,21,Freports of violence.
