OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779217874
OL,3,CA 'significant and sustained police
OL,4,Cresponse is in place' after man was
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FThe victim, a man in his 60s, remains
OL,8,Fin critical condition in hospital, and
OL,9,Fspecialist officers are continuing to
OL,10,Fsupport him and his family.
OL,12,FThere is an increased police presence
OL,13,Fin the Castlefields area and
OL,14,Fsurrounding neighbourhoods, with
OL,15,Fofficers carrying out patrols, house-
OL,16,Fto-house enquiries, extensive searches
OL,17,Fand forensic examinations. We are
OL,18,Fbeing supported by neighbouring forces.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
