PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779217874
OL,3,CA 'significant and sustained police
OL,4,Cresponse is in place' after man was
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Dave Rowlands
OL,8,Fsaid: "I want to reassure the
OL,9,Fcommunity that we are doing everything
OL,10,Fin our power to identify and apprehend
OL,11,Fthose responsible. There is a
OL,12,Fsignificant policing operation
OL,13,Funderway, including increased patrols
OL,14,Fin the area, and I would encourage
OL,15,Fanyone with concerns to speak to our
OL,16,Fofficers.
